<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bạsmk nḥn njtmʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- biạs̊mika naḥ̊nu naj̊tamiʿ̊
 yā rā̊̉sanā ạl̊waḥīd̊
 wāản̊ta maʿ̊nā ḥāḍiruⁿ
 bisẖakẖ̊ṣika ạl̊majīd̊

[V2]
 2- qadi ạr̊tafaʿ̊ta rayĩsaⁿạ
 ʿalaẙnā ạảj̊maʿīn̊
 wāản̊ta qāyỉduⁿ lanā
 birūḥika ạl̊muʿīn̊

[V3]
 3- ạản̊ta ạl̊muʿalĩmu ạl̊waḥīd̊
 ʿalaẙka nas̊tanid̊
 walaẙsa lanā gẖaẙruka
 ʿalaẙhi naʿ̊tamid̊

[V4]
 4- ḥuḍūruka fī was̊ṭinā
 yubadĩdu ạl̊humūm̊
 kālsẖãm̊si ḥīna tusẖ̊riqu
 fatan̊jalī ạl̊gẖuyūm̊

[V5]
 5- wakulũ qal̊biⁿ jāyỉʿiⁿ
 yasẖ̊baʿu min̊ gẖināk̊
 wakulũ ẓāmiⁿ yar̊tawī
 min̊ nah̊ri niʿ̊matik̊

[V6]
 6- ại̹n̊ kāna dẖā surūranā
 ạảmāmaka hunā
 fakam̊ wakam̊ surūrunā
 ladaẙka fī ạlsãmā</lyrics>
</song>